==典礼前==

开幕典礼前几个小时，数位巴西球迷在街头大声歌唱，表达对国家队的支持，人们对揭幕战的兴奋持续高涨。然而，亦有数千人继续示威就举办赛事的约140亿美元的高昂费用作出反对，这使得本届赛事成为世界杯历史上最昂贵的赛事<ref>{{cite news|title=巴西世界杯 史上最贵|url=http://szb.qzwb.com/dnzb/html/2014-05/25/content_674139.htm|accessdate=2014-06-22|newspaper=东南早报|date=2014-05-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140622075010/http://szb.qzwb.com/dnzb/html/2014-05/25/content_674139.htm|archivedate=2014-06-22}}</ref>。圣保罗警方利用[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]驱散示威者<ref>{{cite news|author=尚清|title=巴西世界杯：圣保罗警方与示威者发生冲突|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2014/06/140612_world_cup_clashes.shtml|accessdate=2014-06-22|newspaper=BBC中文网|date=2014-06-12|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912023914/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2014/06/140612_world_cup_clashes.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[圣保罗国际机场|圣保罗国际机场]]的工人封锁了前往机场的道路来发起罢工，要求在世界杯期间增加工资和奖金<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/news/story/_/id/1830732/2014-world-cup-set-most-lucrative-ever?cc=5739|title=World Cup set to be most lucrative ever|date=23 May 2014|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2014-06-22|archive-date=2014-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531182956/http://www.espnfc.com/news/story/_/id/1830732/2014-world-cup-set-most-lucrative-ever?cc=5739|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Record World Cup numbers game for FIFA, Brazil|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2014/05/22/record-world-cup-numbers-game-for-fifa-and-brazil/9458457/|publisher=USA Today|date=22 May 2014|accessdate=2014-06-22|archive-date=2014-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620134155/http://www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2014/05/22/record-world-cup-numbers-game-for-Fifa-and-brazil/9458457/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本次罢工共持续24小时，处于法律原因，工会领导人将本次罢工美其名曰“提早下班<ref name="BBC report">{{cite web |title=World Cup 2014 kicks off with colourful ceremony |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/27779059 |publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=12 June 2014 |accessdate=12 June 2014 |archive-date=2014-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621103314/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/27779059 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。

