开幕典礼持续仅25分钟，为历次世界杯最短<ref>{{cite news|author=范宏基、隋海涛、韩飞、周游|title=明晨巴西世界杯开幕式 历时仅25分钟时间最短|url=http://travel.people.com.cn/n/2014/0612/c41570-25138068.html|accessdate=2014-06-22|newspaper=现代快报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103629/http://travel.people.com.cn/n/2014/0612/c41570-25138068.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。主舞台上660名舞者展现出对巴西自然、人与足球的致敬，球场中央坐落着一枚“活的足球”，由90000个LED灯组成，有7000尼特的亮度<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10894619/World-Cup-2014-opening-ceremony-live.html|title=World Cup 2014 opening ceremony: live|date=12 June 2014|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=13 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622043548/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10894619/World-Cup-2014-opening-ceremony-live.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。表演者装扮成各类树木和鲜花<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/12/world-cup-2014-live-brazil|title=World Cup 2014 opening ceremony – as it happened|date=12 June 2014|work=Guardian|accessdate=13 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613185323/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/12/world-cup-2014-live-brazil|dead-url=no}}</ref>，乐队进行三次独立表演。最后，中间的球缓缓打开，巴西歌手[[克劳迪娅·莱蒂|克劳迪娅·莱蒂]]登场演绎本次世界杯官方主题曲《[[我们天下一家|我们天下一家]]》，随后有份创作该曲的[[嘻哈斗牛梗|嘻哈斗牛梗]]和[[珍妮弗·洛佩兹|珍妮弗·洛佩兹]]登场<ref name="BBC report" /><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2656532/Brazil-2014-World-Cup-gets-underway-opening-ceremony-Arena-Sao-Paulo.html|title=Brazil welcome the watching world as the 2014 World Cup gets underway with Jennifer Lopez and Pitbull performing at the opening ceremony at Arena de Sao Paulo|date=12 June 2014|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=13 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618164643/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2656532/Brazil-2014-World-Cup-gets-underway-opening-ceremony-Arena-Sao-Paulo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。开幕式费用预计约1800万巴西币<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://br.cinema.yahoo.com/blogs/rodrigo-salem/a-abertura-da-copa-do-mundo-foi-mais-cara-que-%E2%80%9Ctropa-de-elite-2%E2%80%9D--onde-o-dinheiro-foi-parar-143939315.html|title=A abertura da Copa do Mundo foi mais cara que “Tropa de Elite 2”. Onde o dinheiro foi parar?|date=13 June 2014|work=Rodrigo Salem|accessdate=13 June 2014|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714232410/https://br.cinema.yahoo.com/blogs/rodrigo-salem/a-abertura-da-copa-do-mundo-foi-mais-cara-que-%E2%80%9Ctropa-de-elite-2%E2%80%9D--onde-o-dinheiro-foi-parar-143939315.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

